You're not pregnant?

362
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:06,780
没有
Nope.

363
00:17:07,120 --> 00:17:09,510
马修和莉莉还一无所知?
An-And Marshall and Lily don't know?

364
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:12,690
后来  我们过来想要告诉你们
Well, afterwards, uh, we came by to tell you guys,

365
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:14,600
可莉莉实在压力很大
but Lily was pretty stressed out, so...

366
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:17,190
