We decided not to say anything till after the wedding.

367
00:17:21,190 --> 00:17:22,640
你们还好吧
You guys okay?

368
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:26,960
这两周当然不会好过 不过...
Well, it hasn't been the easiest two weeks of our lives, but...

369
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:29,010
我们还挺得住
But we're okay.

370
00:17:30,820 --> 00:17:32,560
多亏了那酒吧
The open bar helps.

371
