打扰了  女士
- Excuse me, Miss. - Hi.

372
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,570
能请你跳支舞吗
Could I have this dance?

373
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:40,710
我们都知道这一天终究会来
Well, we knew this day would come eventually.

374
00:17:40,810 --> 00:17:42,510
照顾好她  小绅士
Take care of her, little man.

375
00:17:55,830 --> 00:18:00,450
这是目前为止 你醉得最厉害的一次了
This is by far the drunkest I've ever seen you.

376
00:18:02,630 --> 00:18:04,170
司机
Uh, driver.

377
00:18:06,735 --> 00:18:08,461
Hello!

378
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,750
瑞吉
Ranjit.

379
00:18:09,850 --> 00:18:12,600
回酒店之前能先停一下吗
Hey, can we make a stop before we head back to the hotel?

380
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,850
不用停
You do not have to stop.

381
00:18:14,950 --> 00:18:19,670
你们可以就在后座上办事
You can be together as man and wife right back there,

382
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:22,850
我是好哥们儿
and because we are friends...

383
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,180
我不会偷看的
I will not watch.

384
00:18:26,990 --> 00:18:30,870
不  事实上 我们有别的事要办
Um, no, we actually had something else in mind.

385
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:33,800
当然
Okay.

386
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:36,600
莉莉  去坐下
Lily, go sit down.

387
00:18:37,230 --> 00:18:38,720
欢迎来到维勒饼屋
Welcome to Wienerburger.

388
00:18:38,826 --> 00:18:39,793
Hi.

389
00:18:39,890 --> 00:18:43,420
我要1号餐  别加泡菜
Can we get a number one, please, with no pickles?

390
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:46,910
再来一个4号餐  不要洋葱
And a number four with no onions.

391
00:18:47,010 --> 00:18:49,530
让我猜一下 刚参加完杰斐逊高级舞会?
Let me guess. Jefferson High prom?

392
00:18:49,630 --> 00:18:50,860
不
No.

393
00:18:51,670 --> 00:18:53,200
不过谢谢你
But thank you.

394
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,920
其实  我们刚刚结婚了
Actually, we just got married.

395
00:18:55,020 --> 00:18:58,190
- 恭喜了 - 谢谢
- Wow. Congratulations. - Thank you.

396
00:18:58,290 --> 00:19:00,110
7.80美元
That's $7.80.

397
00:19:01,710 --> 00:19:03,410
- 老兄 - 什么
- Hey, dude. - Yeah.

398
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:07,380
