I don't know how to say this, but your wife just threw up in the trash.

399
00:19:11,740 --> 00:19:13,290
我的妻子
My wife.

400
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:17,920
马修和莉莉终成眷属
So Marshall and Lily were married,

401
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:20,030
罗宾和我却分道扬飙
and Robin and I were broken up.

402
00:19:20,130 --> 00:19:21,810
那时候的确很难过
And as hard as it was at the time,

403
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:23,810
最终我们还是选择了忠于自己
in the end we both got what we wanted.

404
00:19:23,910 --> 00:19:26,780
她如愿去了阿根廷
She did eventually go on to live in Argentina

405
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:29,430
摩洛哥  希腊还有俄罗斯
and Morocco and Greece, Russia,

406
00:19:29,530 --> 00:19:31,390
甚至在日本小住一段时间
even Japan for a little while.

407
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:35,040
而我  则遇到了你们的老妈
And I... well, I met your mom.

408
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:37,760
我深刻地认识到 如果你知道自己想要什么样的生活
I think for the most part if you're really honest with yourself

409
00:19:37,850 --> 00:19:39,480
并且诚实面对自己的心意
about what you want out of life,

410
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,200
那么你会得到想要的一切
life gives it to you.

411
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:47,310
当然  在那一刻 我其实想要一杯威士忌加苏打
Of course, at that moment, all I really wanted was a scotch and soda

412
00:19:47,410 --> 00:19:48,920
再来支雪茄
and a cigar.

413
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:07,410
你和罗宾的事我真的很遗憾
I'm really sorry about you and Robin.

414
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:11,260
我平时总到处开玩笑 希望你们俩分手
I know I was always joking around about wanting you two to break up,

415
00:20:11,290 --> 00:20:14,050
可说实话你们是天生一对
but you were really good together.

416
00:20:14,650 --> 00:20:15,820
是的...
Yeah...

417
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:17,960
的确
we were.

418
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:21,490
只是她不是 命中注定的那一个  你懂吗?
She just wasn't the one, you know?

419
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:24,560
注定的  泰德  够了
The one. Oh, Ted, no.

420
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:28,350
别又跟我说你要重新开始寻找真爱了
Do not tell me you're going to start searching for "the one" again.

421
00:20:28,450 --> 00:20:30,420
只有当我听说你找到注定的那个的时候
The only time I want to hear you saying "the one"

422
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:33,350
再跟我说什么 "姻缘天定"的鬼话  怎么样
