423
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:36,470
不  我要摆脱这一切
No, I need a break from all that, I...

424
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:40,070
我要离开这里 去找点乐子  明白吗
I just want to get out there and have fun for a while, you know?

425
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:41,450
是吗
Really?

426
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:43,360
因为...
'Cause...

427
00:20:44,090 --> 00:20:46,580
你知道吗?你们恋爱已经一年了
you know, you've been in a relationship for a year.

428
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:49,880
你已经有点迟钝了
You're going to... be a little rusty.

429
00:20:51,530 --> 00:20:53,750
- 没错 - 我是说
- Yeah. - I'm just saying...

430
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:57,640
你会需要 需要一点点帮助
you're gonna need, need, need some help out there.

431
00:20:58,040 --> 00:20:59,610
可能吧
Could be.

432
00:21:01,430 --> 00:21:02,720
泰德?
Ted?

433
